291
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:55,000
♪I will face rosy clouds by day♪

292
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,840
♪And lift a torch by night♪

293
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:57,610
Once the bow is drawn,

294
00:16:58,150 --> 00:16:59,220
there's no turning back.

295
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:00,560
