318
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:47,040
♪I want every righteous path on earth♪

319
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:53,840
♪To stand beneath clear skies♪

320
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:22,010
Are you going home?

321
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:24,420
