325
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,570
I heard the Guidance Group was leaving,

326
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,380
and figured

327
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,180
you'd go home to see your folks.

328
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:54,380
Honestly,

329
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,980
when you first arrived

330
00:18:58,590 --> 00:19:00,980
