335
00:19:10,750 --> 00:19:12,140
You think I don't know where you live?

336
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:13,770
You know why

337
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:15,290
I don't go to your place?

338
00:19:16,030 --> 00:19:16,980
To not make you uncomfortable.

339
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,620
I am being the grown-up here, see?

340
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:31,860
I came

341
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,420
because I just wanted to talk with you.

342
00:19:35,070 --> 00:19:36,090
I know it's hard for you

343
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:37,700
that the Guidance Group is leaving.

344
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:41,940
Maybe you don't know,

345
00:19:43,110 --> 00:19:44,290
but you being here these days

346
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,620
really opened my eyes

347
00:19:47,590 --> 00:19:48,660
and made me more perceptive.

348
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,180
Especially you.

349
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:52,420
Even though we were always tense

350
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:53,530
