I don't know about you,

354
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:05,660
but I'm more determined than ever.

355
00:20:08,310 --> 00:20:09,140
So I genuinely want to thank you.

356
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:11,180
Seriously,

357
00:20:12,070 --> 00:20:13,010
from the bottom of my heart.

358
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,140
Here, cheers!

359
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:20,140
Ms. Zheng,

360
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,140
I can't drink anymore.

361
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,380
Alright, alright.

362
00:20:24,750 --> 00:20:25,460
Here, come in!

363
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:29,770
Mr. Wang,

364
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,490
