365
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:32,860
October.

366
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:34,730
Only a few months left.

367
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,380
By then,

368
00:20:36,590 --> 00:20:38,180
you'll probably still be
burning the midnight oil,

369
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,660
working on cases somewhere.

370
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:40,570
But me?

371
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:43,420
I'll be at home, peacefully tending

372
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:44,570
