373
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,700
How about it, jealous of me?

374
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:47,460
Of course.

375
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:50,570
Mr. Wang, I owe you an apology.

376
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:51,570
I feel

377
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,090
I've let you down.

378
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:57,620
I thought bringing you
into the Guidance Group

379
00:20:58,350 --> 00:20:58,660
might

380
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,730
help make things right,

381
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,700
maybe even clear your name.

382
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:05,380
But it all turned out to...

383
00:21:06,070 --> 00:21:07,220
to be for nothing.

384
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:07,980
And you've

385
00:21:08,550 --> 00:21:09,380
worked so hard.

386
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:10,900
I'm truly sorry.

387
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:12,900
Ms. Zheng.

388
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:13,420
Ms. Zheng.

389
00:21:14,590 --> 00:21:15,900
Please don't say that.

390
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:18,050
It's normal

391
00:21:18,590 --> 00:21:20,290
