394
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:25,940
No, no, don't say that.

395
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:26,980
Please don't say that.

396
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:28,140
Mr. Wang,

397
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:31,490
I know I've offended you before,

398
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:32,900
please forgive me.

399
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,490
What are you talking about, Zhang?

400
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,050
You were just doing your job.

401
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,250
I understand.

402
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:39,010
Me, too.

403
00:21:41,590 --> 00:21:42,290
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

404
00:21:42,750 --> 00:21:43,380
Thank you, Ms. Zheng.

405
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:45,810
I've been

406
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,940
holding back a lot of things,

407
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:50,290
and today I want to

408
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,860
let it all out with the help of alcohol.

409
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:53,810
I want to

410
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,010
apply for a transfer

411
00:21:55,510 --> 00:21:56,220
to First Division,

412
00:21:56,550 --> 00:21:56,940
what do you think,

413
00:21:57,270 --> 00:21:58,050
would you take me?

414
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:01,010
Ms. Zheng,

415
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:02,660
this kid's got potential.

416
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,010
Besides, only when young people
are passionate about their work

417
00:22:05,030 --> 00:22:06,140
can they truly do it well.

418
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:08,250
Look at how determined he is.

419
00:22:08,510 --> 00:22:09,460
Just give him a chance.

420
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:10,050
Ms. Zheng,

421
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:11,330
