422
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:12,530
It's not up to me.

423
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:16,050
You need to improve yourself.

424
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:17,700
Eleventh Division

425
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:19,330
