444
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:09,730
in this period.

445
00:23:10,270 --> 00:23:10,730
Thanks.

446
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:13,140
Say hi to Mrs. Wang for me.

447
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:15,810
Alright, I'll take Mr. Wang home.

448
00:23:16,030 --> 00:23:16,980
Go!

449
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:20,250
Mr. Wang, take care.

450
00:23:34,550 --> 00:23:34,940
Hong Liang,

451
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:37,810
we've been buddies
for over twenty years.

452
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,330
How often does life

453
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:43,490
give you that?

454
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:46,770
Good mates like that don't come easy,

455
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:48,460
