463
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:14,050
I guess you don't really want to see me.

464
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,140
So this is goodbye,

465
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:24,090
okay?

466
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:35,900
No matter where you go,

467
00:24:36,110 --> 00:24:37,180
I'll be right here.

468
00:24:38,070 --> 00:24:39,660
If you ever need anything,

469
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:41,620
just tell me.

470
00:24:51,110 --> 00:24:51,570
I'm confident

471
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:54,090
that I've been just

472
00:24:54,920 --> 00:24:55,940
with the Wan Hai case.

473
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,620
If the Guidance Group

474
00:24:57,750 --> 00:25:00,010
is holding on to the Wan Hai case

475
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,380
because you're embarrassed

476
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,330
about failing in the Zhang Wenjing case,

477
00:25:03,550 --> 00:25:05,380
then please go back to the
Provincial People's Procuratorate

478
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:07,090
and ask Mr. Zhang to send another
Guidance Group.

479
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:09,330
I'll fully cooperate
with the new Guidance Group

480
00:25:09,550 --> 00:25:11,180
like I did with the Zhang Wenjing case.

481
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:11,900
Other than that,

482
00:25:12,550 --> 00:25:13,860
