just to get to me?

487
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:23,090
Go on! Investigate me!

488
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:46,140
I was calling my wife

489
00:25:47,350 --> 00:25:48,050
the other day

490
00:25:49,070 --> 00:25:50,090
and was telling her about

491
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:52,250
that student council president election

492
00:25:52,510 --> 00:25:54,010
back when we were in school.

493
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:58,730
Who did Qiao Zhenxing vote for?

494
00:25:58,750 --> 00:25:59,380
Li Renjun.

495
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:01,140
And who did Li Renjun vote for?

496
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,180
Li Renjun as well.

497
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,940
I've been joking about this
for twenty years.

498
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:08,090
After twenty years,

499
00:26:09,350 --> 00:26:10,420
