500
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:12,620
who I voted for?

501
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:16,570
I'll tell you.

502
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:20,900
No, I'm not curious.

503
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:23,810
I don't care who you voted for.

504
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:26,900
What matters is that the student council
made significant progress

505
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:29,180
after I became the president.

506
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:30,490
Just like now,

507
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:33,050
