508
00:26:33,960 --> 00:26:34,860
What truly matters

509
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,660
is that I'll soon
be officially appointed

510
00:26:36,790 --> 00:26:37,700
as the Prosecutor-General

511
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,290
of the Dongping People's Procuratorate,

512
00:26:40,030 --> 00:26:41,810
and I'll uphold justice

513
00:26:42,030 --> 00:26:43,730
and the rule of law better than ever.

514
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:44,700
This isn't

515
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:46,940
just my oath as a prosecutor,

516
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,220
but what I truly believe in.

517
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:57,940
Good luck.

518
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,090
It's pointless telling you this.

519
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:10,860
Safe travels.

520
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:09,620
When are you leaving?

521
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:10,810
It's fine.

522
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,250
I can stay with you a bit longer.

523
00:28:13,350 --> 00:28:14,940
I mean when are you resigning?

524
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:16,980
Weren't you going to be a lawyer?

525
00:28:21,590 --> 00:28:22,570
I haven't decided yet.

526
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:25,730
Yeah, you do need to think it through.

527
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,140
Young people gotta be cautious

528
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:29,730
when looking for jobs,

529
00:28:30,240 --> 00:28:30,860
just like with dating.

530
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:35,940
Ms. Zheng,

531
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,860
you must really dislike me.

532
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:41,940
You can tell?

533
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,570
Why would I dislike you,

534
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:48,460
silly?

535
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:49,530
I know,

536
00:28:51,000 --> 00:28:52,330
I'm not as smart as Mr. Hong,

537
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:54,900
or as experienced and insightful

538
00:28:55,070 --> 00:28:55,860
as Mr. Wang.

539
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:57,730
And compared with Zhang,

540
00:28:58,510 --> 00:28:59,490
even though we're both young,

541
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,660
he's much more focused

542
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:02,660
and enthusiastic.

543
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:05,380
I'm nowhere near him.

544
00:29:06,590 --> 00:29:07,050
Ms. Zheng,

545
00:29:08,350 --> 00:29:10,460
I have obtained four certificates,

546
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:12,700
but

547
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,180
I still don't know what I want to do.

548
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:16,660
I just want to leave here.

549
00:29:18,310 --> 00:29:19,620
Don't take it the wrong way,

550
00:29:20,070 --> 00:29:22,180
