so constrained like you.

551
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:24,220
I want to be able to
afford nice clothes,

552
00:29:24,510 --> 00:29:26,220
and nice makeup,

553
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:27,250
I...

554
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:28,140
You want to make more money.

555
00:29:32,350 --> 00:29:33,620
There's nothing wrong with
wanting to make more money.

556
00:29:34,550 --> 00:29:35,730
I want that too!

557
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,490
Nobody's better or worse for it.

558
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:38,900
Honestly, Ziyan,

559
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,460
life is your own.

560
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:44,570
Find a way that works for you

561
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:46,940
and make the best of it.

562
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,460
I respect your choice.

563
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:54,330
You've been with me for a long time,

564
00:29:54,790 --> 00:29:55,860
so I know you very well.

565
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:57,460
You hold yourself

566
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:59,620
to high standards,

567
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:01,460
so no matter where you go

568
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:02,620
or what you do,

